                  <Text layoutX="55.0" layoutY="1008.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Animation today plays a vital role not just in entertainment, but also in education, advertising, social media, gaming, and public service. Animations are used in Filipino classrooms to explain lessons, in commercials that promote products, and in public safety campaigns. Learning animation empowers students to become not just consumers, but creators. In this chapter, you will explore how animation has evolved globally and locally, and why learning it today can open many creative and career opportunities for you in the Philippines and beyond." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
